fields.name: Cardio Workout Plan
fields.description: Cardio exercise is any exercise that raises your heart rate. Face it our bodies were made to move. And we all know that to keep our muscles in shape we need move them. This movement makes them stronger and stronger muscles make for a more efficient and healthy body. Your heart is a muscle. Therefore working it makes it stronger. A stronger cardio-vascular system means more capillaries delivering more oxygen to cells in your muscles. This enables your cells to burn more fat during both exercise and inactivity. We have some wonderful plans which will get your blood pumping and build up your fitness.

fields.name: Leg Workout Plan
fields.description: Strong legs do more than look good. Even the simplest daily movements like walking require leg strength. This means that incorporating leg workouts into your routine is integral to your health. But you may wonder where to begin. Whether you’re working out at home pandemic-style or back at the gym sweating it out, creating an effective leg workout doesn’t have to be complicated. With our plan you can get the defined legs you have been dreaming about.

fields.name: Upper Body Workout Plan
fields.description: Upper body resistance or strength training has a long list of benefits. It helps you boost muscle strength and endurance in your arms, back, chest, and shoulders. It also helps you burn calories, reduce your risk of injury, and build stronger bones. Here at Shuffle Fitness we have some incredible resources to help tone your upper body.

fields.name: Vegan Nutrition Plan
fields.description: This vegan nutrition plan, is for those, who are wanting to change their lives through nutrition and exercise, but want to do so without any animal bi-product.

fields.name: Vegetarian Nutrition Plan
fields.description: The vegetarin nutrition plan, is great for those who want to be healthy but keep dairy in their overall nutrition journey. There will be lots of delicious food that are healthy and full of flavour.

fields.name: Meditation and Mindfulness Plan
fields.description: This plan is to teach its participants how to activate their breathing, and settle into the moment when stress triggers begin to surface in their lives.

fields.name: 21 Days to Rewire Your Brain Plan
fields.description: This plan is to help those understand how the power of their thoughts can help them manage stress, break unhealthy patterns, and overcome all mental/emotional, and spiritual obstacles.
